originalText: I will cull you in the name of Tchort.
Culling is too good for you!
Feral mongrel! I'll make you bleed for this!
::Gasps for air.:: You knocked... my... air... out...
I can't... move... I... I... Hnnnn...
I feel... it... in... my... bones...
I can't see! Tchort guide me!
Where in the name of Tchort are you!?
My brain is being crushed! Ugggh!
Can't pull... the wretched thing out!
I think I can see the bone!
Don't let me go down... like this... Tchort...
I'm taking... you down with me... ah...
It burns! Make it stop! Arrrgh!
Put it out! Put it out!
::Frantically tries to pat the fire out.::
Tchort wishes that I cull... cull you all.
A great culling is upon us!
I don't wish to be culled!
Spare my life, I beg of you!
I think my rib is broken...
No! Get out... GET OUT OF MY... HEEEEEAAAAD!
Oh, you won't have me. You! Won't! Have! Meeeee-heheh!
Brrrr! Grrrr! There is an intruder in my... my... mind! Aaargh!
You have been selected... for culling!
It's the end of the line for you, inbred!
You should not exist. Tchort commands me to correct this mistake of nature.
Creatures like you must not be allowed to breed...
You'll regret the day you left the womb!
Don't worry, it'll all be over soon...
Resistance is futile... Tchort's will must be done.
Where do you think you are going, feral mongrel?
Come on, you're not going to sleep now, are you?
Wake up, I'm not done with you yet, mutt!
You don't look all too well.
Oh, yes... I'm back in action!
Let's see what you're made of!
I'll beat you to a bloody pulp!
I'll kick your inbred ass all the way to the Surface.
I'll carve you up like a mushroom cake!
Let's put a bloody smile on that ibred face!
I've saved this one just for you.
Stay still. It'll all be over soon...
You'll be gone in a puff of smoke! ::Laughs.::
Nothing will remain of you, inbred!
Don't worry, it'll be quick and very painful...
Not even your bones will remain.
I'll turn you into red swill!
Tchort has a present for you...
See if you can catch this, mongrel!
I shall pin you to a wall, inbred!
I've got the bolt just for you!
I'll crush your puny little mind...
Your weak mind doesn't stand a chance...
I'll turn your brain to mush!
Now you see me, now you don't.
Do you like your bones chilled?
Your mongrel hide won't save you from this!
It's a cold end for you, abomination!
How about I burn that smile off your face!?
Let's heat things up a bit...
I hope you'll enjoy this warm reception...
No one will be able to fix ya after I'm done with you!
I need some help over here!
Your time... is in my hands, inbred!
Time will not be kind to you.
This is going right through you!
One limb at a time, one limb at a time...
I'll blow your head to bits!
